## Non-Negotiable Tech Rules

- local-first
- no cloud requirement
- no hidden scraping
- no trainer file modification
- raw runs are source of truth
- source adapters normalize benchmark definitions
- UI must not hardcode Voltaic logic
- analysis logic must be testable outside React components
